body: On July 2, 2021, we denied your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190144997. We sent you a denial notice that explains why we denied your case and your options. Please follow the instructions in the notice. If you do not receive your denial notice by July 17, 2021, please go to www.uscis.gov/e-request to request a copy of the notice. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Card Was Delivered To Me By The Post Office
body: On June 23, 2021, the Post Office delivered your new card for Receipt Number YSC2190144998, to the address that you gave us. The tracking number assigned is 9205590153708408447160. You can use your tracking number at www.USPS.com in the Quick Tools Tracking section. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

body: As of June 9, 2021, fingerprints relating to your Form I-751, Petition to Remove Conditions on Residence, Receipt Number YSC2190144999, have been applied to your case. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
